"""Test method to get currency conversion request url."""
amount = 10
from_currency = 'USD'
to_currency = 'EUR'
req_url = currency._get_currency_req_url(amount, from_currency, to_currency)
exp_req_url = 'https://www.google.com/finance/converter?a=10&from=USD&to=EUR'
